0xFC30DDFF.name: GET_ENTITY_POPULATION_TYPE

params.name: entity
params.description: the entity to obtain the population type from

0xFC30DDFF.description: This native gets an entity's population type.
0xFC30DDFF.resultsDescription:
Returns the population type ID, defined by the below enumeration:```cpp
enum ePopulationType
{
	POPTYPE_UNKNOWN = 0,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_PERMANENT,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_PARKED,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_PATROL,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_SCENARIO,
	POPTYPE_RANDOM_AMBIENT,
	POPTYPE_PERMANENT,
	POPTYPE_MISSION,
	POPTYPE_REPLAY,
	POPTYPE_CACHE,
	POPTYPE_TOOL
};
```
